{"tid":292253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[歡迎補充]熱血公民洗底大軍醜聞結集","createTime":"2017-06-21T08:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T06:30:49.000Z","uid":51754,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"452f494849898095ed227e015a0fc1bd5b51ae3b","tid":292253,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗依家想靠做區洗底，我地要認住呢班當公眾白痴嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打絲打有更多資料補充就即管貼出嚟啦，開嚟見我！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>鄭錦滿　鄭松泰議員助理</strong><br />\n<br />\n葵涌廣場火燭打卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/b0pmDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fb0pmDc.jpg&h=e31f9cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱血時報：民建聯區議員火場抽水自拍　無恥行為惹網民怒插（原文已刪）<br />\n<a href=\"http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:tQ8_bQtbXIgJ:www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-22-2016/31217+&amp;cd=1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3AtQ8_bQtbXIgJ%3Awww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-22-2016%2F31217%2B%26cd%3D1%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ct%3Dclnk%26gl%3Dhk&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b019e066\" target=\"_blank\">http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:tQ8_bQtbXIgJ:www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-22-2016/31217+&amp;cd=1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk</a><br />\n<br />\n講大話老屈本民青「掃黃」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=312087209246055&amp;set=a.119211015200343.1073741827.100013343350817&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D312087209246055%26set%3Da.119211015200343.1073741827.100013343350817%26type%3D3%26theater&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6368109a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=312087209246055&amp;set=a.119211015200343.1073741827.100013343350817&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n------<br />\n<strong>黃敬業　阿公岩社區主任（東區）</strong><br />\n<br />\n熱血時報清算派主持「傳道人」「關愛座獵人」三國人物<strong>陳到</strong><br />\n<br />\n「關愛座獵人」陳到（神駒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155183999472254&amp;set=a.276140562253.190273.653277253&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10155183999472254%26set%3Da.276140562253.190273.653277253%26type%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=177cf627\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155183999472254&amp;set=a.276140562253.190273.653277253&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1</a><br />\n<br />\n廁所門口搞「居民大會」（陳興旺）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=311785562609553&amp;set=ecnf.100013343350817&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D311785562609553%26set%3Decnf.100013343350817%26type%3D3%26theater&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=588604c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=311785562609553&amp;set=ecnf.100013343350817&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好我係陳到，筆名黄敬業，係青蒜派始祖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/289684/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/289684/page/1</a><br />\n------<br />\n<strong>鍾雪兒　屏山南社區主任（元朗）<br />\n<br />\n青城派霍由佳</strong><br />\n<br />\n[網上遊魂被起底] 霍由佳真名鍾雪兒 ─ 鄭松泰議員辦事處屏山南社區主任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/289436/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/289436/page/1</a><br />\n------<br />\n<strong>梁逸朗　田景社區主任（屯門）</strong><br />\n<br />\n上城大編委莊「烽凌」，選兩次先選到<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民時任「首領」黃洋達同「皇后」陳秀慧入埋城大幫佢拉票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongyeungtat/videos/1069833939745918/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongyeungtat%2Fvideos%2F1069833939745918%2F&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1cb0fe82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongyeungtat/videos/1069833939745918/</a><br />\n<br />\n編委任內用Facebook功能吞併沿用多年嘅編委專頁，搞到舊報導無晒<br />\n------<br />\n<strong>黃學凱　山景社區主任（屯門）</strong><br />\n<br />\n電郵地址&quot;huang&quot;，疑似係支那人？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/121326_bf2df2bc036a99a0c5497f418cc4302f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F121326_bf2df2bc036a99a0c5497f418cc4302f.jpg&h=37e80b09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a53563bd8b815c4cc8f0e17a8befb088d5a51522","tid":292253,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"先俾個正皮再跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734be70e43cbc3e98a2c1cfba5869098c2e27dbb","tid":292253,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"支持建立DATABASE"},{"pid":"f6b4fcd53ccedd734f136b3e185c552b9ef02996","tid":292253,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6b5c1cf68168c4c38fd845d10a89697e1d7b46ce","tid":292253,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持建立DATABASE</blockquote><br />\nfb咪有個香港癲佬xx"},{"pid":"7f350dc316c76f8fc76e03a48d021bd364c1619d","tid":292253,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持建立DATABASE</blockquote><br />\nfb咪有個香港癲佬xx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n集中討論果班社區主任，好多名字都好陌生，同一般熱狗形象有好大分別"},{"pid":"ae3f631232f55bf597a1ec8ee8ad0f295aaf9715","tid":292253,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"仲未知有幾多狗落左區，挖晒出來先慢慢整理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bc69a99b3e9211b5b8b7533a4360928906b974","tid":292253,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:44: